	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-174356305" class="story-title"> <a   href="//slashdot.org/story/24/07/01/1528252/french-antitrust-regulators-preparing-nvidia-charges">French Antitrust Regulators Preparing Nvidia Charges</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/french-antitrust-regulators-preparing-nvidia-charges-sources-say-2024-07-01/"  title="External link - https://www.reuters.com/technology/french-antitrust-regulators-preparing-nvidia-charges-sources-say-2024-07-01/" target="_blank"> (reuters.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
